在函数体开头 (1888 取 model 之前) 插入早返回, 在唯一构造点 1894 之前拦截:

```rust
fn build_agent_runtime(
    job: &AgentJob,
) -> Result<ConversationRuntime<AnthropicRuntimeClient, SubagentToolExecutor>, String> {
    // P8 safety gate (v0.4.16): subagents are not yet routed to OpenAI-family
    // executors. EXECUTOR_PROVIDER=="openai" is the exact value apply_to_env
    // (config.rs:145) writes for provider openai/custom (every OpenAI-compatible
    // menu provider collapses to this literal). Without this gate an
    // OpenAI-family main session would SILENTLY build an Anthropic client below
    // and bill the user's Anthropic OAuth/Keychain credential. Fail loud.
    // Exact-match mirrors resolve_openai_executor_config (openai_executor.rs:359):
    // no trim, no lowercase — so the detection set equals the real routing set
    // and never misfires on anthropic / anthropic-compat (Category A/B).
    if std::env::var("EXECUTOR_PROVIDER").as_deref() == Ok("openai") {
        return Err(
            "subagents currently require an Anthropic-family executor; \
             OpenAI-family subagent dispatch lands in v0.4.17. \
             Your main session is unaffected."
                .to_string(),
        );
    }

    let model = job
        .manifest
        .model
        .clone()
        .unwrap_or_else(|| DEFAULT_AGENT_MODEL.to_string());
    // ... 其余 1893-1902 一字不动
}
```

关键点:
- 1894 是生产代码里唯一构造 AnthropicRuntimeClient::new 的地方 (4409 那处在 #[cfg(test)] 内), 一处早返回即覆盖全部 subagent dispatch。
- 用 `.as_deref() == Ok("openai")` 精确镜像 resolver 的 `provider != "openai"` 语义 (不 trim 不 lowercase)。注意 var() 返回 Result<String,VarError>, .as_deref() 得到 Result<&str,&VarError>, 与 Ok("openai") 比相等成立。
- 错误文案故意不含 ANTHROPIC_API_KEY / EXECUTOR_API_KEY / OPENAI_API_KEY 任何字样 (避免泄漏 + 与现有 Category C Anthropic-auth 文案区分), 且明确 "Your main session is unaffected" (主会话 OpenAI executor 路由不经过 build_agent_runtime, 早已工作)。

配套:
- CHANGELOG 加一条 v0.4.16 条目: OpenAI-family 主会话下 subagent 暂明确报错 (此前静默盗刷 Anthropic 凭据), 完整 OpenAI 子代理路由 v0.4.17 落地。
- 无 Cargo.toml 改动, 无新 import (std::env 已大量使用)。

